data.description: Heating system is 3 zoned high-efficiency. Pool needs to have new heater and pump, structurally pool is in good condition. Home has huge storage on second floor attic/walk-in.
data.whatILove: Tons of space with 6 bedrooms, 3.5 baths and 3 car garage! Come check out this great neighborhood on Ogden's East Bench! This home has newer roof, updated windows, central A/C. *swimming pool, and 6 bedrooms plus an office. Kitchen is massive and has all updated Hickory Cabinets, center island and plenty of storage including a large pantry. Master has walkout sliding door to pool-yard area. Call to schedule your showing today. Make this your perfect home with a little TLC and needs new carpeting. No telling if the pool functions and filling in may be best option. Please call Rob #480-612-4523 for showing.
